messages.messageBody:
http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/interactive/timelines/british/index.shtml

My husband, Keith, just sent this link to me.

Americans get a little gaga about British TV, but I have to say that
some of the websites from the U.K. are truly wonderful.

This is a timeline you can set for all of Britain or just England,
Wales, Scotland or Northern Ireland (in later years).

I'm going to add it to my history page. http://sandradodd.com/history


If people here have other favorite history sites not already there
that are fun and different, please share them here!

Sandra
